detail.name: Hit
detail.effect: [When Attacking] Add up to 1 card from your life to your hand. Then, choose up to 1 of your opponent's Battle Cards and it gets -5000 power for the turn.

detail.name: ヒット
detail.effect: [アタック時]自分のライフ1枚までを手札に加える。その後、相手のバトルカード1枚までを選び、このターン中、パワー-5000。

faq.question: When this card's [When Attacking] skill activates, can you choose 1 of your opponent's Battle Cards and give it -5000 power without adding 1 card from your life to your hand?
faq.answer: Yes. You can choose 1 of your opponent's Battle Cards and give it -5000 power even if you don't add 1 card from your life to your hand.

faq.question: このカードの【アタック時】を発動した時、ライフ1枚を手札に加えずに、相手のバトルカード1枚を選び、パワー−5000できますか？
faq.answer: はい、ライフ1枚を手札に加えなくても、相手のバトルカード1枚を選び、パワー−5000することができます。
